description: Construction of one building of 44 storeys (within the existing consented envelope - PA/05/00052), one building of 30 storeys (within the existing consented envelope - PA/05/00052) and two buildings of eight storeys to provide 802 dwellings, and a total of 3,267sq.m of retail (A1, A2, A3), Office (B1) and Community Uses (D1) at lower ground, ground and level 1, 5833 sq.m plant, public spaces and parking. (The application is accompanied by an Environmental Impact Assessment).
